In December 2003, documents seized from Jackson's personal assistant revealed a link to an alleged crime involving Miko Brando.
The indictment accuses Jackson of planning to abduct a child, falsely imprison someone, and extort another.
Cash movements align with the charges.
Despite facing child molestation allegations, Jackson expressed love for his fans and criticized a disrespectful video.
